'''Potentially upcoming features''' are unreleased or unannounced features that may be added to VRChat in the future. They are identified through discovery in tools such as the [[VRChat API]] or platforms like Crowdin, through public statements by VRChat staff, or by appearing in A/B testing. Anything on this page should be taken with a grain of salt; appearing here does not confirm that a feature will be added.

Entries will typically be removed from this page when they are either confirmed (through being given an applicable testing branch on [[Open Beta]], or being fully released) or removed after being denied through official VRChat sources.

