=== Discovery and social system improvements ===

[[File:For-You-Discovery-Page.jpg|thumb|Earlier "For You" world list experiment]]
[[File:Discover-Alpha-Live-Tab.jpg|thumb|Discover (Alpha) on the Live tab of the Main Menu]]
VRChat stated it is exploring improvements to discovery and social systems so users can find intended communities while naturally separating audiences that should not interact.<ref name="TrustSafety2025Blog" /> No specific features or timeline were announced.

In a developer stream Q&A on {{Date|May 29, 2026}}, the team described a personalized "For You" world list as an experiment that was running at the time, noting that users may see it, see variations of it, or not see it at all, and that no further details would be shared while the experiment was in progress.<ref name="ForYouWorldList">[https://ask.vrchat.com/t/may-29-developer-stream-q-a-summary/48500 "May 29 Developer Stream Q&A Summary"] on ''ask.vrchat.com''; posted June 1, 2026; retrieved June 9, 2026.</ref>

As of {{Date|July 2026}}, the "For You" world list was no longer observed in the client.

An A/B test labeled Discover (Alpha) has been observed on the Live tab of the Main Menu. First observed {{Date|2026-07-24}}.

